high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter to the left of the black bin.
Pick up the salt shaker in front of the mustard.
Move to the counter to the left and look up at the cabinets.
Open the cabinet door, place the salt shaker inside the cabinet, close the door.
Turn around and walk to the counter with the coffee maker on it on the left.
Pick up the salt shaker from the counter.
Walk back over to the counter to the right of the sink and look back up at the cabinet.
Open the cabinet door, put the salt shaker inside of the cabinet to the right of the first salt shaker, close the door.
anns.task_desc: To move two salt shakers to the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right, proceed to counter.
Pick up salt shaker from counter.
Turn left then right to face counter with pot on it.  Look up to cabinets above.
Open cabinet, put shaker on lowest self.  Close cabinet.
Turn around, go to counter with coffee maker on it.  Turn left to face counter.
Pick up salt shaker off of counter.
Turn left, go to counter with pot on it.  Look up to cabinets above.
Open cabinet, put shaker directly to the right of the first shaker, close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Move two shakers to a cabinet.
